    <Placemark><name>Doolin Cafe</name><description>Good veg options, fresh-baked goods. Best proper food in the village. Doolin</description><styleUrl>#food</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>-9.3785,52.9965</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
